  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 12 Guests</strong></p>
<p>Situated at the top of Plagne 1800, the Chalet Madeleine is a charming and traditional chalet with a light and airy feel throughout.</p>
<p>This elevated position gives the chalet panoramic views of the surrounding mountains and valley below, which can be enjoyed from the balcony and terrace. The open plan living area gives the chalet a light and airy feel, and is the perfect place to unwind after a long day on the slopes. Bedrooms are virtually all en suite and comfortably furnished to a high standard. A private sauna and shower room on the lower ground floor provide the perfect place to relax. For your convenience to get to the lifts each morning, there is a <strong>free </strong>Inghams minibus to take you directly to the lifts of Plagne Centre - a 2 minute drive away.</p>]]></description>
